title: Benihana with D'Arcy Carden
itunes:title: Benihana with D'Arcy Carden
description:
Actor and comedian D'Arcy Carden (The Good Place, Barry) to review and discuss her childhood relationship to this week's chain, Benihana. Plus, discussions about favorite autumn eats and snacking habits on sets before getting into a Halloween edition of Cereal.
